snippet.title: ABSOLUTE MATTER // Reveal Trailer // 1st Person PvX MMO
snippet.description:
Absolute Matter (formerly The Invitation) is a tactical extraction shooter all about player interaction. In this high stakes PvX game both the players and the environment dynamically create quests.

You can wishlist Absolute Matter on Steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2114540/Absolute_Matter/

To get in touch with us please join our discord:
https://discord.gg/9DCEAfz
...or Timos stream: 
https://www.twitch.tv/tool1_timo

For more information our website is the way to go: 
https://absolute-matter.com
